channel.title: Haunted-Isle Development Team
channel.description:
Hello, welcome to the Haunted-Isle Development thread. Haunted-Village has seen enough days and was a complete sucess. I would like to start a development team to create a new server called "Haunted-Isle." Which will be the first in its series. What I will do is put together a Coding Team and a Testing Team. If you would like to join please leave an application here in this format.
[code][b]Position:[/b] [i]Put the position you want to join here. (Coder/Tester)[/i] [b]Reliability:[/b] [i]Indicate whether or not you will be a reliable person.[/i] [b]Time Zone:[/b] [i]I need to know your time zone so I can call for people at good times[/i] [b]Experience w/ Selected Position:[/b] [i]Indicate your personal experience with your selected position[/i] [b]Experience Proof:[/b] [i]Please give some evidence that you have done something of the sort before[/i] [b]Contact Option:[/b] [i]Please give me some form of contact that I can reach you at[/i][/code] *Note* - Please keep in mind, I will pick the best that fit the position. Even if someone posts to help before another, I may choose someone over that person.
Here are the positions and their current members: -----------------------------------------------
Coders: ------- 1.Legend Rene 2. 3.
Testers: -------- 1.~Dioem 2.Chaos Corps 3.doggiedoo86 4.Pur3_G3_Pk3r 5.nonten 07
Thank you, Coder Quack
Server Features added: Nature and Fire Rune crafting from one altar Full Gem Crafting Cooking by clicking Fire Remains Prayer Exp from altar. Full Mining. Nature and Fire Runecrafting. Staffs Stand Straight up. Make air fire earth and water battlestaffs and get crafting xp and smithing along the way.
